summary: You can buy Strong Potions and Poisons even at level 1 in alchemist shops of Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
Why alchemists hide their strong potions and poisons from you at Level 1? and they will sell them when your level is Up?
That's the problem.
This mod Unlevels alchemist shops of Skyrim. So you can buy strong potions and poisons even at Level 1.
and you can spend your money for better things!
It's another little step to make game like morrowind.
author: hr75
